<h3 class="date"><a href="/2009/jan/12/">&#x27a0;</a> January 12, 2009</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="elements-spam" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://mcsweeneys.net/2008/12/30roeder.html">The Elements of Spam.</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Form the possessive of nouns by adding &#8216;s, just an apostrophe, just an s, a semicolon, a w, an ampersand, a 9, or anything.  &#8220;My wifesd*porcupine hot pix for u.&#8221;</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
                    Filed under
                    
                        : <a rel="tag" class="tag" href="/tag/funny/">funny</a>
                    
