    <div class="well" id="hotmails-antispam-measures" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.theregister.co.uk/2007/05/01/hotmail_friendly_fire/">Hotmail&#39;s antispam measures snuff out legit emails, too | The Register</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>I&#8217;ve been experiencing this &#8212; Emails I send to HoTMaiL users are getting silently swallowed, neither bouncing nor ending up in their Spam folders.</p>

