<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/aug/16/">&#x27a0;</a> August 16, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="fuzzyocrplugin" >

        
        <a name="002876"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://wiki.apache.org/spamassassin/FuzzyOcrPlugin">FuzzyOcrPlugin - Spamassassin Wiki</a></h4>

        

        <p>SpamAssassin plugin which OCRs the images attached to image-only mails to work out if they contain text like V14GRA.  I imagine this is massively CPU-intense, but it might be worth looking at.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
